        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/1061425612/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Silverlight spotted in the wild" src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1192/1061425612_6a84bbbf24_m.jpg" height="225" width="240" /></a>

