            <p><a href="http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/news/gameday_recap.jsp?ymd=20070808&amp;content_id=2137880&amp;vkey=recap&amp;fext=.jsp&amp;c_id=bos">This</a> is the first time I've seen Microsoft's Flash-killer <a href="http://www.microsoft.com/silverlight/">Silverlight</a> plugin used on a genuine, non-Microsoft-demo website.  MLB are using it to play video.</p>

